      <title>波多黎各公用事业债券持有人寻求更大的破产赔付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/puerto-rico-utility-bondholders-seek-bigger-bankruptcy-payouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波多黎各破产电力公司的债券持有人正在敦促法院增加他们的追偿金额，因为新的预测显示，由于用电量增加，该公司的收入可能会超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/puerto-rico-utility-bondholders-seek-bigger-bankruptcy-payouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:13:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
