      <title>DEA 将重新分类大麻的报告导致大麻库存飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pot-stocks-surge-on-report-dea-is-moving-to-reclassify-marijuana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国缉毒局将大麻重新归类为危险性较低的药物类别后，大麻相关公司的股价周二大幅上涨，这对该行业来说将是一个历史性的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/pot-stocks-surge-on-report-dea-is-moving-to-reclassify-marijuana</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 17:45:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
